OL,3,CJenrick asks top civil servant to
OL,4,Cinvestigate Attorney General
OL,6,FThe Government's top civil servant has
OL,7,Fbeen asked to investigate "potential
OL,8,Fconflicts of interest" in relation to
OL,9,Fministers' top legal adviser.
OL,11,FConservative shadow justice secretary
OL,12,FRobert Jenrick has written to Cabinet
OL,13,FSecretary Sir Chris Wormald to request
OL,14,Fan investigation into Attorney General
OL,15,FLord Richard Hermer KC as a result of
OL,16,Fhis previous legal work.
