OL,3,CJenrick asks top civil servant to
OL,4,Cinvestigate Attorney General
OL,6,FMr Jenrick raised questions about four
OL,7,Fof Lord Hermer's previous cases, which
OL,8,Fhe proposed could raise potential
OL,9,Fconflicts of interest in his work with
OL,10,FGovernment.
OL,12,FThese included "representation of
OL,13,FGerry Adams in matters related to the
OL,14,FLegacy Act" and "representation of
OL,15,FAfghan families in the ongoing
OL,16,FAfghanistan Inquiry".
