OL,6,F"These rules sit alongside rigorous
OL,7,Fand long-standing protocols to ensure
OL,8,Fall Law Officers are not consulted on
OL,9,Fissues that give rise to conflicts of
OL,10,Finterest."
OL,12,FIt comes after the Attorney General
OL,13,Ffaced questions last week over his
OL,14,Frole in the Government's proposed
OL,15,Frepeal of legislation that put a stop
OL,16,Fto civil claims from Troubles
OL,17,Finternees such as Mr Adams.
