OL,6,FLast week Lord Hermer came under fire
OL,7,Fwhen questioned by MPs for refusing to
OL,8,Fconfirm whether he had advised the
OL,9,FGovernment on repealing the laws.
OL,11,FLord Hermer told the Commons Justice
OL,12,FCommittee that convention for law
OL,13,Fofficers under the ministerial code
OL,14,F"precludes" him from saying whether he
OL,15,Fhad been asked to advise on any
OL,16,Fmatters or detail any advice given.
