OL,6,FPressed by Conservative committee
OL,7,Fmember Sir Ashley Fox in a lengthy
OL,8,Fexchange on Wednesday morning, he also
OL,9,Fsaid he could not "recall" if he acted
OL,10,Ffor Mr Adams on "any form of
OL,11,Fconditional fee agreement".
OL,13,FHe said: "I did represent Gerry Adams
OL,14,Fon something unconnected to the Legacy.
OL,16,F"As it happens, as a reflection of our
OL,17,Flegal system, at the same time I was
OL,18,Frepresenting the family of a young
OL,19,FBritish soldier murdered by the IRA in
OL,20,Fthe 1970s.
